%% Session phase state machine
%% Sources: docs/view-specs/home.md, new-session.md, part-out-import.md, part-out-reconciliation.md,
%%          list-cups.md, list-lots.md, feature/part-out-coordinator/product-spec.md
%%
%% XML export and Bricklink mass update occur in updating_inventory, after organizing.

stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR

    [*] --> importing: "POST /sessions (New session submit - 201 only)"
    importing --> counting: "POST .../part-out/confirm (Confirm and begin counting)"
    counting --> reconciling: "Compare with Part-Out List (POST .../sessions/{id}/phase; any joined worker)"
    reconciling --> organizing: "Declare ready to organize (POST .../sessions/{id}/phase)"
    organizing --> updating_inventory: "Declare ready to import (POST .../sessions/{id}/phase)"
    organizing --> reconciling: "Return to reconciling (POST .../sessions/{id}/phase)<br>organizer progress preserved"
    updating_inventory --> closed: "Mark session complete (POST .../sessions/{id}/phase)"
    closed --> [*]

    note right of importing
        Only session-scoped screen.
        SessionNav hidden.
        Post-join route /session/:id/import
        Inline fetch ok or error after 3 retries
        (422 invalid set: no session, stay on New session)
    end note

    note right of counting
        Default landing Lot form.
        SessionNav visible (Home Lot Lots Reconcile; Cups).
        Workers record lots and browse cups.
        Reconcile nav: diff preview; Compare with Part-Out List advances phase.
    end note

    note right of reconciling
        Initial count and sort activity done.
        Compare included part-out lines vs lot counts.
        Edit lots and Resolve every line explicitly.
        Declare ready to organize when all rows resolved.
        Post-join route /reconciliation
        List cups still browsable via SessionNav Cups.
    end note

    note right of organizing
        Split and print pick lists for workers.
        Workers put parts away into storage.
        Mark lines moved or needs location.
        Mark organizer lists complete.
        Declare ready to import when all lists complete.
        Post-join route /lots?mode=organizer
        List cups still browsable via SessionNav Cups.
        SessionNav Reconcile visible counting through updating_inventory.
        Return to reconciling preserves pick-list Moved/New loc checks.
    end note

    note right of closed
        Session routes redirect Home.
    end note

    note right of updating_inventory
        Reconciled — export XML (phase unchanged).
        Worker verifies and submits on Bricklink manually.
        Mark session complete → closed.
        Post-join route /reconciliation
        SessionNav Cups hidden.
    end note
